  "reference_number": "RUS1689",
  "remarks": "\n Colonel Georgy Ivanovich SHUVAEV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Colonel SHUVAEV is a member of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation; he has held the position of Head of Missile Troops and Artillery of the 1st Tank Army since 2019. There are therefore reasonable grounds to suspect that Colonel SHUVAEV is an “involved person” per regulation 6(2)(a)(i) by “actively destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine” in that he works for the Government of Russia as a Colonel General of the armed forces of the Russian Federation, thereby fulfilling regulation 6(4A)(i).\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
